      "text": "string list（字符串列表）",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:264",
      "text": "将约束该 job 所有 command 的 limit 名称。limit 会限制带有该 limit name 的 command 的并发执行数量。",
      "ascii_letters": 36,
      "cjk_chars": 23
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:267",
      "text": "job 内该 task 的唯一 string id。",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:268",
      "text": "refersto",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:271",
      "text": "minslots",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:274",
      "text": "maxslots",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:278",
      "text": "string list（字符串列表）",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:279",
      "text": "environment key name 列表，用来建立该 command 将运行于其中的环境。",
      "ascii_letters": 25,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:280",
      "text": "retryrcodes",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:281",
      "text": "integer list（整数列表类型）",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:282",
      "text": "会触发该 command auto-retry logic 的 return code 列表。",
      "ascii_letters": 31,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:283",
      "text": "metadata",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:285",
      "text": "command 的用户定义 metadata。",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:286",
      "text": "resumewhile",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:287",
      "text": "string list（字符串列表）",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:288",
      "text": "由 blade 执行的 command argument list，或 special keyword 列表；任一者都会决定该 command 是否可 resume。",
      "ascii_letters": 51,
      "cjk_chars": 18
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:289",
      "text": "resumepin",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:291",
      "text": "一个 boolean 值，表示 command 在 resume 时是否应在同一 host 上运行。",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:292",
      "text": "minrunsecs",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:295",
      "text": "maxrunsecs",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:298",
      "text": "Invocation 调用记录属性",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:301",
      "text": "description",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:304",
      "text": "该 invocation 所属 job 的唯一 identifier 标识符。",
      "ascii_letters": 23,
      "cjk_chars": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:307",
      "text": "该 invocation 所属 task 的唯一 identifier 标识符。",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:310",
      "text": "该 invocation 所属 command 的唯一 identifier 标识符。",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:313",
      "text": "Invocation Identifier，即 command 内 invocation 的唯一 identifier 标识符。",
      "ascii_letters": 47,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:316",
      "text": "如果这是最新 invocation，则此 boolean 值为 true。当 task 被 retried 时，任何现有 invocation 都不会被视为 current。",
      "ascii_letters": 49,
      "cjk_chars": 23
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:317",
      "text": "numslots",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:319",
      "text": "该 invocation 使用的 slot 数量。",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:321",
      "text": "string list（字符串列表）",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:322",
      "text": "invocation 正在使用的 limit 列表。如果 engine 被重启，此值用于从当前正在运行的 invocation 重建 limit counter。",
      "ascii_letters": 43,
      "cjk_chars": 26
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:323",
      "text": "starttime",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:324",
      "text": "timestamp（时间戳类型）",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:325",
      "text": "invocation 的开始时间。",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:326",
      "text": "stoptime",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:327",
      "text": "timestamp（时间戳类型）",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:328",
      "text": "invocation 的停止时间。",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:331",
      "text": "invocation 的 process id 进程标识符。",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:334",
      "text": "进程 resident set size，单位为 GB。",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:337",
      "text": "进程的 memory usage，单位为 GB。",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:340",
      "text": "进程的当前 CPU utilization。",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:341",
      "text": "elapsedapp",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:343",
      "text": "进程的 elapsed user time，单位为秒。",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:344",
      "text": "elapsedsys",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:346",
      "text": "进程的 elapsed system time，单位为秒。",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:347",
      "text": "elapsedreal",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:349",
      "text": "进程的 elapsed wall-clock time，单位为秒。",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:352",
      "text": "进程的 return code 返回代码。",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:353",
      "text": "retrycount",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:355",
      "text": "invocation 运行时 task retry counter 的值。如果 task 曾在某个时间点变为 active，task retry 或 job restart 会递增它。",
      "ascii_letters": 55,
      "cjk_chars": 21
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:356",
      "text": "resumecount",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:359",
      "text": "resumable",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:361",
      "text": "如果 command 可以 resume，则此 boolean 值为 true。",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:364",
      "text": "invocation 的 command 正在运行或曾运行所在 blade 的 bladeid。",
      "ascii_letters": 29,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:368",
      "text": "description",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:371",
      "text": "blade 名称。它是 blade 的唯一 identifier 标识符，通常是该 blade 的 hostname。",
      "ascii_letters": 33,
      "cjk_chars": 15
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:377",
      "text": "blade 正在监听的 port number。",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:380",
      "text": "blade 运行所在 operating system 的名称。",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:381",
      "text": "osversion",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:383",
      "text": "blade 运行所在 operating system 的版本。",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:384",
      "text": "boottime",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:385",
      "text": "timestamp（时间戳类型）",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:386",
      "text": "host 的 boot time 启动时间。",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:389",
      "text": "host 的 CPU/core 数量。",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:392",
      "text": "host 的 CPU load average。",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 1
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:393",
      "text": "availmemory",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:395",
      "text": "host 的 available memory 可用内存，单位为 GB。",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:396",
      "text": "availdisk",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:398",
      "text": "host 的 available disk space 可用磁盘空间，单位为 GB。",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:401",
      "text": "Tractor blade 版本。",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:404",
      "text": "blade 使用的 profile name 配置档名称。",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:407",
      "text": "blade 的 NIMBY 状态。",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:408",
      "text": "starttime",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:409",
      "text": "timestamp（时间戳类型）",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:410",
      "text": "blade process 的开始时间。",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:411",
      "text": "numslots",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:413",
      "text": "blade 上的 slot 总数数量。",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:416",
      "text": "blade 的 Universal Desirability Index（通用期望指数），用于帮助某些 blade 比其他 blade 更早被分配 task。值越高，blade 被分配工作的机会越高。",
      "ascii_letters": 50,
      "cjk_chars": 34
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:419",
      "text": "blade 的 status note 状态说明。",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:420",
      "text": "heartbeattime",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:421",
      "text": "timestamp（时间戳类型）",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:422",
      "text": "blade 上次联系 engine 的时间。",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:425",
      "text": "blade 的 universally unique identifier 通用唯一标识符。Over time（随着时间推移），hostname、port 和 IP address 等属性可能会被不同 host 复用。填充 invocation record 时使用此 id，以便永久正确识别运行该 command 的特定 blade。",
      "ascii_letters": 95,
      "cjk_chars": 46
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:426",
      "text": "cleartime",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:427",
      "text": "timestamp（时间戳类型）",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:428",
      "text": "用户请求清除 blade data 的时间。只有 heartbeattime 大于 cleartime 的 blade 才会在 dashboard 中可见。",
      "ascii_letters": 45,
      "cjk_chars": 20
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:429",
      "text": "gpulabel",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:431",
      "text": "Blade host GPU 信息。",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:433",
      "text": "Job 和 task 可以指定与 command 相关的 attribute value。这些 attribute 包括",
      "ascii_letters": 37,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:436",
      "text": "maxslots",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "34f70bdcf7:439",
      "text": "。在 command 级别定义的 value 会覆盖 task 和 job 级别指定的 value；在 task 级别定义的 value 会覆盖 job 级别指定的 value。",
      "ascii_letters": 41,
      "cjk_chars": 29
    }
  ],
